        "message": "LU-1760 utils: Avoid Mis-leading LNet self test error message\n\nExecuting \"lst new_session\" when lnet-selftest module is not yet\nloaded can create confusing error messages like \"Invalid parameters\nlist in command line\".\n\nThis change attempts to load the lnet-selftest module from the\n\"lst new_session\" command on error, and tries again to create the\nsession.\n\nSigned-off-by: Doug Oucharek <doug@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ic66c6b6d552c981fe5f753fc70a358b768ae0497\n"
